metadata.name: Blueberries Haunt My Headspace
metadata.description:
Salvador Dalí and I were reminiscing the other day about how wonderful it can be to enjoy fresh blueberries by the sea on a warm summer day. 

Of course this happened in my head, but who's to say its not real?

This image is part of my digital collaborations series - A Digital Dalí collaboration using my own work as an initialization image in DiscoDiffusion with "painted by Salvador Dalí" included in the text prompt.
